OKLAHOMA SOUTHERN TRUST, an Express Trust, and A. J. Diffie, v. SECURITIES AND EXCHANGE COMMISSION. No. 2016. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. April 22, 1940. Elmer J. Lundy and Logan Stephenson, both of Tulsa, Okl., for appellants. Chester T. Lane, Gen. Counsel, Securities and Exchange Commission, and Christopher M. Jenks, Asst. Gen. Counsel, Securities, and Exchange Commission, both of Washington, D. C., for appellee.

Before PHILLIPS, BRATTON, and HUXMAN, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Cause remanded, judgment of the district court entered October 3, 1939, vacated, and proceeding dismissed per stipulation.
